      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car enthusiasts! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream. I\u2019ve spent countless weekends keeping this beauty in top-notch shape, and it really shows\u2014it\u2019s practically in showroom condition! From the gleaming paint to the spotless interior, it\u2019s clear this car has been pampered its whole life. It drives as smooth as the day I got it, and honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find another one this clean. I\u2019m looking for a buyer who will love it as much as I have. Come by and take a look; I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
