      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3, meticulously optimized for the discerning pilot. This S54 powerplant breathes through polished individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band that screams to its 8,000 RPM redline. We\u2019ve addressed the critical failure points with a comprehensive Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and a structural subframe reinforcement kit, ensuring the chassis handles the increased torsional rigidity of the upgraded polyurethane bushings. The suspension features a bespoke coilover setup with rebound and compression adjustment tailored for a neutral turn-in. Finished in a depth-defying Carbon Black metallic, this specimen retains factory-spec compression across all six cylinders. It\u2019s not just a car; it\u2019s a mechanical symphony calibrated for peak lateral Gs and surgical precision. Turn-key and ready for the canyon or the collection, this unit has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment with zero expense spared on its drivetrain integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
